{"pid":"b148078f5ba6cb183e5e279b45c24a13db0f0c5b","tid":1687270,"uid":77526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:29:43.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"05e0180b8b9b611b1dc88badae619533a1cefaaa","tid":1687270,"uid":68110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"曱甴平 甴近平 甴曱平<br />\n我冇野講"},{"pid":"5d6d399049ce83ae7ee9f0560913b8851a5a3761","tid":1687270,"uid":154950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"係48小時內<br />\n頭幾個鐘佢慢慢同你搞手續<br />\n其實只要大約拉左十個鐘 又冇教好訓<br />\n咁思考能力會弱好多<br />\n<br />\n我冇野講係對自己一個保障 <br />\n保障自己唔會因為唔夠精神亂講野<br />\n<br />\n唯一缺點係上庭帶機會問你做咩落口供果陣唔講 上到庭先講 <br />\n<br />\n但到時好多方法合理解釋 交返俾你律師"},{"pid":"b8052fb4fbad7f5cbdb6d2d0215ead829f0ba6b0","tid":1687270,"uid":14370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"112. 我無野講"},{"pid":"25a11b7c8b42d28bfe6d900114d8271d00762fa0","tid":1687270,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"好精簡，推"},{"pid":"ead69e1e4f762c57e217971b352c08ecf015b746","tid":1687270,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"借黎開Post"},{"pid":"626acd96a1ffec47631093b3a474cf24e50327c4","tid":1687270,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"甴總"},{"pid":"ab4a832726f766acf7cbd2bf3c41a0cfa9b4dfde","tid":1687270,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<br />\n<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"db9e35249ae66d93a07900b7c956d6e40fdf69a4","tid":1687270,"uid":42542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"29707627fb50f6547341b125923bd9f3337464b7","tid":1687270,"uid":239117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"26f5fa1c4fef0c95853532